(36, 0, 'Zephaniah', 'Zeph', 3, null, 36, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Zep', '~zephaniah~zp~zep~zeph~ze~', null, null, '<p>Although Zephaniah has many sub-themes, the great theme of Zephaniah is the coming Day of Yahweh, the Great Tribulation, and judgment that will come on the earth. Zephaniah 1:2 speaks of this Day with hyperbolic emphasis. Zephaniah also mentions the blessings experienced by Israel in the Millennial Kingdom which follows after the Tribulation (cp. Zeph. 3:19-20).</p>'),
